{"name":"Sylvie’s Grilled Smoked Salmon Pizza","slug":"sylvie-s-grilled-smoked-salmon-pizza","description":"Entertaining outside just got easier with this simple, quick grilled pizza – a favourite of Epicure’s President and Founder, Sylvie Rochette.","ingredients":[{"name":"Basic Pizza Dough","quantity":"1 recipe prepared","additionalInstruction":"or 2 store-bought (10 in) pizza shells"},{"name":"dry yeast","quantity":"1 pkg","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"warm water","quantity":"1 cup","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"sugar","quantity":"1 tsp","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"Sea Salt","quantity":"<sup>1</sup>&frasl;<sub>2</sub> tsp","additionalInstruction":"ground"},{"name":"all-purpose flour","quantity":"2 <sup>1</sup>&frasl;<sub>2</sub> cups","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"olive oil","quantity":"2 tbsp","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"olive oil","quantity":"2 tbsp","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"crème fraîche, or sour cream","quantity":"1 cup","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"Lemon Dilly Dip Mix","quantity":"2 tbsp","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"smoked salmon","quantity":"<sup>1</sup>&frasl;<sub>2</sub> lb (225 g)","additionalInstruction":"thinly sliced"},{"name":"red onion","quantity":"1","additionalInstruction":"thinly sliced"},{"name":"baby spinach","quantity":"2 cups","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"Chili Flakes & Garlic Topper","quantity":null,"additionalInstruction":"to taste – optional"}],"totalTime":"25 min","servings":"16 servings","preparation":["If using Basic Pizza Dough, lightly flour work surface and form dough into 2 — 10” pizza rounds. Loosely cover with a tea towel or plastic wrap and set aside.","Preheat grill to medium-high.","For the sauce, mix together crème fraîche and Lemon Dilly Dip Mix. Set aside.","Using a basting brush, lightly oil one side of the dough.","Place oiled side down on grill. Grill with lid closed 3–5 minutes, or until grill marks appear on bottom. Alternative